{"tid":32764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔見張單晒馬攞衫 一男子涉刑恐洗衣店被捕","createTime":"2016-12-10T11:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T20:43:19.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09fd1e6b7810afd84ccac538c464de1ab8069666","tid":32764,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>唔見張單晒馬攞衫 一男子涉刑恐洗衣店被捕</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-12-10 19:08:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n調景嶺都會駅商場，下午5時許，一名男子到上址一間洗衣店取回已洗衣服時，一時忘記帶單據到場，要求店員通融被拒後，先與店員對罵，其間自稱是黑社會成員，並電召找來十多名大漢到場恐嚇店員，店員見狀報警求助。警方接報手持警棍盾牌到場，勒令大漢一字形排於牆邊接受調查，警員經調查後以涉嫌刑事恐嚇拘捕該名鬧事男子，帶署調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a31b233f9ac14ea22be43ab409ecc75a72602b","tid":32764,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584fcf6172893ac15cc402653be037f5ed320205","tid":32764,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:23:20.000Z","msg":"咩年代呀 仲黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1cadc673276f06e827f6c27dfbd0d5963ca414","tid":32764,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗帶晒警棍盾牌呀"},{"pid":"77f4cddd88a718a4f81b8df3512a1b92663600a1","tid":32764,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:26:14.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為乜啊"},{"pid":"948233f28ecc30fb3e25f7bd7e8edcf8fd87f33a","tid":32764,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:03:37.000Z","msg":"都會駅果間野本身態度好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h